        <title type="html"><![CDATA[解决Zotero或者PaperShip绑定坚果云WebDAV时，出现验证失败的问题]]></title>
        <id>https://sprswa.github.io/post/jie-jue-zotero-huo-zhe-papership-bang-ding-jian-guo-yun-webdav-shi-chu-xian-yan-zheng-shi-bai-de-wen-ti/</id>
        <link href="https://sprswa.github.io/post/jie-jue-zotero-huo-zhe-papership-bang-ding-jian-guo-yun-webdav-shi-chu-xian-yan-zheng-shi-bai-de-wen-ti/">
        </link>
        <updated>2020-04-11T13:47:50.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://sprswa.github.io/post-images/1586613866996.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
解决办法是：<br>
打开坚果云官网，登录坚果云账号，在zotero文件夹下新建空白的lastsync.txt文件。<br>
务必注意的是，必须使用坚果云自带的新建文本文档工具来建立lastsync.txt文件，不能通过手动上传的方式。</p>
<p><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/b2kuoqPqEYOGb9i_cvFa4Q">参考文章</a></p>
]]></content>
    </entry>
